GetDataFromAccountSettingAccountID: SELECT as2."Acronym", as2."CompanyURL", as2."ModifiedDate" FROM aisdm."AccountSetting" as2 WHERE "AccountID" = $AccountID;
GetDataFromAccountAuthenticationSetting: SELECT aas."AccountAuthenticationSettingID", aas."JWT", aas."ModifiedDate" FROM aisdm."AccountAuthenticationSetting" aas WHERE "AccountID" = $AccountID;
GetDataFromAccountApplicationAuthenticat: SELECT aaas."IPEnabled", aaas."AnonymousOrgAuthEnabled", aaas."ModifiedDate" FROM aisdm."AccountApplicationAuthenticationSetting" aaas WHERE aaas."AccountAuthenticationSettingID" = (SELECT aas."AccountAuthenticationSettingID" FROM aisdm."AccountAuthenticationSetting" aas WHERE "AccountID" = $AccountID);
GetDataFromPublisher: SELECT * FROM aisdm."Publisher" p WHERE p."Name" = '$Name';
GetCollectioncriteriatype: SELECT * FROM aismm."ebs_pricing_pim_mapping" p WHERE p."item_type" = '$itemtype';
